the first time.

31:09.168 --> 31:11.468
Right.

31:11.470 --> 31:13.370
Okay, main vessels
are dissected.

31:13.372 --> 31:15.138
Stapler.

31:16.207 --> 31:18.141
(stapler clicks)

31:21.246 --> 31:23.247
Mets.

31:25.984 --> 31:28.252
(beeping)
one more snip.

31:32.490 --> 31:34.992
Okay, we're clear.
Reycraft.

31:34.994 --> 31:36.660
Okay, all right.

31:36.662 --> 31:39.162
Come to papa.

