on your vocal cords.

34:38.510 --> 34:40.377
Can you fix it?

34:40.379 --> 34:44.247
'cause I <i>love</i> kathleen turner
as much as the next guy, but...

34:44.249 --> 34:46.183
Yeah, we booked you
for surgery on Wednesday,

34:46.185 --> 34:48.385
