the whole deal.

35:13.412 --> 35:16.746
I'll do it.

35:16.748 --> 35:19.716
No. You won't.

35:20.885 --> 35:22.419
I cancelled
the open house.

35:22.421 --> 35:24.621
What? Bridgette, why?

35:24.623 --> 35:26.656
Because louie,
you're a mess.

35:26.658 --> 35:28.258
I just watched
your shin bone

35:28.260 --> 35:29.726
Pop out of your leg
this morning.

35:29.728 --> 35:31.561
And believe me, that's gonna
give me nightmares

35:31.563 --> 35:33.163
For a long time.

35:33.165 --> 35:35.332
Good.
Louie.

35:37.602 --> 35:40.504
I'm sorry.

35:40.506 --> 35:41.805
Me, too.

35:41.807 --> 35:43.573
And I wanna help you.

35:43.575 --> 35:47.544
You need a place to recover,
and we still have the house.

35:47.546 --> 35:49.646
