up with a personal support work

35:53.652 --> 35:55.285
If you'd rather do that.
That's--that's--

35:55.287 --> 35:57.521
No, I wanna do it.
I'm gonna do it.

35:57.523 --> 36:00.390
Just till you're back
on your feet.

36:00.392 --> 36:03.894
(sighs) louie,
you need a friend right now.

36:03.896 --> 36:06.630
And I was really good
at being your friend.

36:08.900 --> 36:11.701
Why don't we let you two
figure out the details.

36:11.703 --> 36:14.237
Let's do that. Okay.

36:24.615 --> 36:26.750
(inhales deeply)

36:44.936 --> 36:49.539
